// Paper Information Page Paper Examples: • Newspaper • Cup • Cardboard Box • Book • Printer Paper • Greeting Card • Egg Carton How to Identify: • Generally Easy to Bend • Pencil marks are easy to see on paper • Generally white or brown in color How to Recycle: • Most town/city recycling facilities accept paper in their trucks • Grocery stores may accept paper bags • Large cardboard boxes can be thrown into large junk bins Ideas to Reuse: • Printer paper can be used for origami and crafts • Cardboard boxes can be used to package other items and ship them • Paper can be used for rough work and other homework assignments
